# =============================================================================
# .copilotignore — Exclude noise from GitHub Copilot CLI context
# =============================================================================
# Reduces context pollution by hiding build artifacts, generated files,
# secrets, and large non-code assets from AI analysis.

# --- Build artifacts & caches ---
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/.next/
**/build/
**/.turbo/
**/.cache/
storybook-static/
artifacts/
coverage/
code-cov/
TestResults/
**/bin/
**/obj/

# --- Secrets & environment files ---
.env
.env.*
*.key
*.pem
*.p12
*.pfx
**/appsettings.Development.json
**/appsettings.Production.json

# --- Generated & lock files ---
package-lock.json
tsconfig.tsbuildinfo
nul

# --- Large assets & non-code ---
readme/
logs/
**/*.png
**/*.jpg
**/*.jpeg
**/*.gif
**/*.svg
**/*.ico
**/*.woff
**/*.woff2
**/*.ttf
**/*.eot

# --- IDE & tool configuration ---
.vscode/
*.code-workspace
settings.VisualStudio.json
